Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是生氣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真以為要被扒層皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說「我要離家出走」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「做得到你就試試～」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是你一言我一語就吵起來了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這個我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個浴巾呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這個也睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有多渴望睡個好覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能一直離家出走的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說也不能不去學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話該你說麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃過一次就會越來越麻煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.12,0:00:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一天的話沒啥影響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒事所以一天天逃下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來自己已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…這種事還真輪不到我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.15,0:00:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒白當家裡蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算自己很難過的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也盡考慮別人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧你！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是這樣 只考慮別人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間還要更…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和雪集也曾經談過…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直都被芽間束縛著…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她現在就在我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 沒有相信芽間的事情啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…啊不…也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買了咖哩牛肉哦 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,520元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱牛肉撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是你想那樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來看日記…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的咖哩牛肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就知道芽間的願望了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 開始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的芽間在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所不知道的芽間的心事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:23.52,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(664,257)}今天和大家一起玩了 很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:32.16,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(614,257)}今天和大家一起玩了 很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩句話除了「很好玩」「很高興」 就沒的不同了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 很不擅長寫作文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這裡稍微不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今天和大家一起玩時摔倒了 好痛」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這裡也不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「今天和大家一起去探望仁碳媽媽了」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探望…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 還真是經常去呢 大家結伴一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳的媽媽一直在醫院呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 給神仙寫信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請讓仁碳的媽媽早日恢復健康」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼給？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.74,explain,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}註：龍勢是一種煙花，像火箭一樣升天，還有一些會內置降落傘等機關 吉田町每年10月的第二個週日會舉辦龍勢祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大家決定一起做煙花了」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我覺得好難」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不過我會加油」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「給煙花火箭裡放封信 送給神仙吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 就是這個吧？芽間的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候說要做 結果還是沒成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了…我媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳什麼的 我才不理他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜裡吃飯的話要變豬的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給你變豬的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹹味拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加蛋花…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿健拉麵沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想餵你點吃的 哄哄你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸快回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃快點兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不要跟來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來「啊～」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再做奇怪的事咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼逃學還穿制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…沒什麼不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搭配都是我的自由吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花火藥的購買和使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據「火藥管理法」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要18歲以上有國家認證才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想鑽空子的話 玩具煙花還有點可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也要執照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…果然沒辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常想想 做煙花確實是需要認證的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 昨天整理房間的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是認真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集大量煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆開取出火藥全部集中到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放進廁紙芯裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會燃起來所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然的吧 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 小孩好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得這是能行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前即使是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也覺得真能飛起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真以為會比龍勢祭上看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛得更高更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時覺得高中生什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去就像是很厲害的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無所不能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得那個時侯 真是什麼都做的到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先找找有沒有什麼可行的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本辦不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算做了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一不是你說的芽間的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是徒勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟在你那兒的芽間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好確認過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能害怕向她本人確認吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間感覺似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.91,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(718,623)}Deja Vu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是跑前面的宿海和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目送他遠去的可憐的雪集君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有說出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是那傢伙說要到秘密基地集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…好像是芽間提出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被芽間打電話叫出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 她好像說要商量什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易想起來的 為什麼不說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為宿海在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原話是「瞞著宿海集合吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.00,title_no,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(382,251)}第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.00,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(277,422)}真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.00,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,390)}願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識會做的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我工作場所有個大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在祭典的時候擔任煙花師傅的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 仁太 你想做煙花嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問為什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和波波他們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那我就去拜託他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳仁碳仁碳仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.89,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}康達爾城出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 要我先跟他聯繫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事情到時再說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就算是簡單的也要用這麼多的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是我不想給你們做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我還沒見過那麼多錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒問題 總能搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和安鳴拚死地打工就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 別擅自決定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嘛 互相幫助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 安鳴一周干足七天的話絕對沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊 我還什麼都沒說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…幹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…幹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也幹 打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是輸入金額的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是二手貨的價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新品的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 在這裡輸入差價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你一瞬間就學會了我一個月才掌握的技能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也花太多時間了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「荒銀光臨」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你就完全不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 果然是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 傳說中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有打工的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校卻請假麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個不是沒去上課的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 怎麼回事 他們兩個有啥關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡 迎—光 臨——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那傢伙幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是和以前一樣沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.01,0:13:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我膠布 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿…海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接好了 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准這麼叫！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花的事情他們好像是認真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 我們要不要也捐點錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要陪著宿海不務正業嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想管的話我也算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可以出來一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝個茶什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要考試了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是學年第四呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學年第二的在胡說什麼呢 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪你可是件很痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳回得太晚了 不良少年！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳絕對有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上很快就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.27,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上出門也很迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗專題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小狗是母的 那仁碳就絕對在做奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:39.18,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}啊～茄子醃得真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的小狗 小奧斯卡 母 7歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈巴狗啊 好可愛 身上的褶好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:46.42,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}小奧斯卡是點心店的招牌狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:51.45,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}它會跟小客人們打招呼 表示「歡迎光臨」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:56.13,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}多虧了小奧斯卡 來光顧的客人多了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:57.65,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}老婆婆也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在簽名簿上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:02.70,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}今天小奧斯卡也希望自己能夠精神百倍 笑容滿面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 仁太君退學了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊 但是為什麼那樣說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 問了奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是前段時間 我看見他好像在打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太他 有沒有跟父親交待清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們家尊重個人的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都交給仁太他自己決定 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題 有問題 有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 波波 我今天沒有排班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長好像很喜歡那傢伙的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上是和你一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 羊山的工地？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:16:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這活不會太重了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 要掙錢的話體力活是首選
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭煙花可是和錢一起飛走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望…芽間的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多考慮一下自己的事情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不爽啊 你那態度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說雪集和鶴見子他們有沒有跟你聯絡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 時常會有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼在意仁碳的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 仁碳就仁碳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是那麼叫的嗎 有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫仁碳的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人 那邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然了 仁碳他 可是很帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在芽間不考慮自己事情的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仁碳…一直在想幫芽間著想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小心腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便變動燈光的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風能吹動照明燈嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃閃發光的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽做的味道…很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 仁碳 上學很辛苦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說不定很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…沒想到比宅在家裡要舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種「活著」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…「活著」…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那個 不是說實際上的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是到現在為止的我…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間也覺得 看到有種「活著」感覺的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也有種「活著」的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我把訂金帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過能請你先幫忙做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個啊 抱歉不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心和祭典的幹事說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後幹事就訓了我一頓 說「居然去幫什麼高中生」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是拚命在努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰啊 那個幹事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接去找他面談
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…本間家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽間家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他姐 仁太他們 似乎為了你在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
